"><figure class="media-object-image img-header"><div class="image-container responsive-media"><img width="700" height="460" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-823344?width=700&amp;height=460" alt="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><figcaption class="imageCaption"></figcaption></figure></div></div></div><div class="articleBody" data-sbid="WP-WSJO-0000022794"><div class="clearfix bylineWrap"><div class="byline">华尔街日报图书工作人员</div><time class="timestamp article__timestamp flexbox__flex--1">美国东部时间 2023 年 7 月 26 日下午 4:16 </time></div><div subscriptions-actions="" subscriptions-display="NOT data.noSharing"><div class="share-bar"><amp-social-share type="system" width="72" height="24" data-param-url="https://www.wsj.com/articles/12-books-to-read-the-best-reviews-of-july-7eb37ce4"></amp-social-share></div></div><section subscriptions-section="content"><p> 《华尔街日报》评论家讨论的七月最值得关注的书籍精选。 </p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
