"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/completely-mad-review-across-the-ocean-with-an-oar-5afb65c0?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">完全疯狂：汤姆·麦克莱恩、约翰·费尔法克斯和史诗般的单人划船横渡大西洋的比赛</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
